{"type":"dialog","id":21},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"好渴......喉咙像是被火烤着......","id":22},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"......究竟有多长时间了......？","id":23},{"type":"dialog","id":24},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.6","block":"true","id":25},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/37/Avg_ac1_4.png","x":"0","y":"0","xScale":"1","yScale":"1","fadetime":"0","screenadapt":"cvoerall","id":26},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"false","id":27},{"type":"imagetween","xFrom":"0","yFrom":"0","xTo":"0","yTo":"-20","xScaleFrom":"1","yScaleFrom":"1","xScaleTo":"1.1","yScaleTo":"1.1","duration":"15","block":"false","id":28},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":29},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d0/Avg_bg_bg_med.png","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":30},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_009","name2":"avg_npc_009","focus":"1","fedetime":"1","block":"true","id":31},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":32},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赏金猎人","text":"真厉害啊，都被吊在这一天多了，真亏她能忍得住啊。","id":33,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_009.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_009","name2":"avg_npc_009","focus":"2","id":34},{"type":"dialogue","name":"粗暴的赏金猎人","text":"喂，你们可别把她搞死了，宝藏的位置她还没说呢！","id":35,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_009.png"},{"type":"character","id":36},{"type":"dialog","id":37},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":38},{"type":"image","fadetime":"0","id":39},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"false","id":40},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_003","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":41},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":42},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可萝尔","text":"......我不会.....不会告诉你的......","id":43,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/88/Avg_avg_npc_003.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_009","id":44},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赏金猎人","text":"别给她水喝，直到她说了为止！","id":45,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/c8/Avg_avg_npc_009.png"},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":46},{"type":"dialog","fadetime":"0","id":47},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":48},{"type":"background","id":49},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":50},{"type":"character","id":51},{"type":"dialog","id":52},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":53},{"type":"dialog","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可萝尔","text":"我会死......吗？","id":55},{"type":"character","id":56},{"type":"dialog","id":57},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":58},{"type":"dialog","id":59},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":60},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":61},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":62},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"......","id":63},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"没想到就算到了卡西米尔。","id":64},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"胡作非为的歹徒也是哪里都有。","id":65},{"type":"dialog","id":66},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d0/Avg_bg_bg_med.png","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":67},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_008","id":68},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赏金猎人","text":"嗯？哪里来的家伙，不想活了吗？","id":69,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/58/Avg_avg_npc_008.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_007","id":70},{"type":"dialogue","name":"粗暴的赏金猎人","text":"喂，小子，你赶紧给我——","id":71,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/cd/Avg_avg_npc_007.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":72},{"type":"playsound","key":"$b_char_defboost","volume":"0.7","id":73},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"20","block":"false","id":74},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":75},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":76},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":77},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_007","id":78},{"type":"dialogue","name":"粗暴的赏金猎人","text":"唔，好，好疼。","id":79,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/cd/Avg_avg_npc_007.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"粗暴的赏金猎人","text":"仔细看，他这身装扮......不像是当地人啊。","id":80,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/cd/Avg_avg_npc_007.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_008","id":81},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赏金猎人","text":"管他是哪里来的！他就一个人，不过是来送死的！","id":82,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/58/Avg_avg_npc_008.png"},{"type":"character","id":83},{"type":"dialog","id":84},{"type":"character","name":"char_220_grani#5","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":85},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":86},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"所以，得把你们全部解决掉才行？","id":87,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_char_220_grani_5.png"},{"type":"character","id":88},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_008","id":89},{"type":"playsound","key":"$b_char_defboost","volume":"0.7","id":90},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"20","block":"false","id":91},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":92},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":93},{"type":"dialogue","name":"粗暴的赏金猎人","text":"噗啊！","id":94,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/58/Avg_avg_npc_008.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_007","id":95},{"type":"playsound","key":"$b_char_defboost","volume":"0.7","id":96},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"20","block":"false","id":97},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":98},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":99},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赏金猎人","text":"咕......","id":100,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/cd/Avg_avg_npc_007.png"},{"type":"character","id":101},{"type":"dialog","id":102},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":103},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":104},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":105},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$m_dia_street_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta3_181101/m_dia_street_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","crossfade":"1","id":106,"musicid":1},{"type":"character","name":"char_220_grani#3","id":107},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"好了，他们一时半会还醒不过来，我们赶紧离开这里。","id":108,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d6/Avg_char_220_grani_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_003","id":109},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可萝尔","text":"你......你是......","id":110,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/88/Avg_avg_npc_003.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_220_grani#3","id":111},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"别怕，没有人能再伤害你了，我会带你离开。","id":112,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d6/Avg_char_220_grani_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_003","name2":"char_220_grani#3","focus":"1","id":113},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可萝尔","text":"——","id":114,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/88/Avg_avg_npc_003.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可萝尔","text":"抱歉，我、我的头......好晕......","id":115,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/88/Avg_avg_npc_003.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_003","name2":"char_220_grani#3","focus":"2","id":116},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"你脸色不太好。没关系，让我抱着你。","id":117,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d6/Avg_char_220_grani_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"请抓紧了。","id":118,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d6/Avg_char_220_grani_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_003","name2":"char_220_grani#3","focus":"1","id":119},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可萝尔","text":"嗯.....","id":120,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/88/Avg_avg_npc_003.png"},{"type":"character","id":121},{"type":"dialog","id":122},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_soldiersrun","id":123},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":124},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/50/Avg_bg_bg_county_1.png","fadetime":"1","id":125},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":126},{"type":"dialogue","name":"","text":"晴 \\ 能见度 14公里","id":127},{"type":"dialogue","name":"","text":"某村庄内","id":128},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":129},{"type":"dialog","id":130},{"type":"character","id":131},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_008","name2":"avg_npc_005","focus":"1","id":132},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赏金猎人","text":"你有没有看到一个拿长枪的小子？","id":133,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/58/Avg_avg_npc_008.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_008","name2":"avg_npc_005","focus":"2","id":134},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村民","text":"我一直待在家里，外面发生什么我不知道。","id":135,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_008","name2":"avg_npc_005","focus":"1","id":136},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赏金猎人","text":"要是让我知道你窝藏了他们，有你好看的！","id":137,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/58/Avg_avg_npc_008.png"},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_soldiersrun","id":138},{"type":"character","id":139},{"type":"dialog","id":140},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":141},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":142},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":143},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$m_dia_street_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta3_181101/m_dia_street_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","crossfade":"1","id":144,"musicid":2},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村民","text":"————","id":146,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","id":147},{"type":"dialog","id":148},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":149},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村民","text":"那群家伙已经离开了，格拉尼骑警小姐，你们可以从壁橱里出来了。","id":150},{"type":"character","id":151},{"type":"dialog","id":152},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":153},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":154},{"type":"character","name":"char_220_grani#3","fadetime":"1","id":155},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":156},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格拉尼","text":"嘿~！","id":157,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d6/Avg_char_220_grani_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格拉尼","text":"又被大叔帮了大忙啊。","id":158,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d6/Avg_char_220_grani_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005","id":159},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村民","text":"可萝尔你没事吧？真是苦了你了。","id":160,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_003","name2":"avg_npc_005","focus":"1","id":161},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可萝尔","text":"卢克大叔，多谢你，我现在好多了。","id":162,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/88/Avg_avg_npc_003.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_220_grani#3","id":163},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格拉尼","text":"因为有大家的帮助，我才能救出你。","id":164,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d6/Avg_char_220_grani_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_003","name2":"avg_npc_005","focus":"2","id":165},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村民","text":"可萝尔，不要担心！","id":166,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村民","text":"骑士小姐已经和我们商量好了！她一定会拯救整个村子的！","id":167,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_003","id":168},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可萝尔","text":"啊？小姐？","id":169,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/88/Avg_avg_npc_003.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_003","name2":"char_220_grani#2","focus":"2","id":170},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格拉尼","text":"这，是啊，我是女孩子啊。","id":171,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/8f/Avg_char_220_grani_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_003","name2":"char_220_grani#2","focus":"1","id":172},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可萝尔","text":"啊？","id":173,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/88/Avg_avg_npc_003.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_003","name2":"char_220_grani#1","focus":"2","id":174},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格拉尼","text":"唔！就算是我，也是有女孩子的自尊心的！","id":175,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e0/Avg_char_220_grani_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_003","name2":"char_220_grani#1","focus":"1","id":176},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可萝尔","text":"欸、欸，对不起。","id":177,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/88/Avg_avg_npc_003.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可萝尔","text":"......","id":178,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/88/Avg_avg_npc_003.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可萝尔","text":"虽然看穿着不像......","id":179,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/88/Avg_avg_npc_003.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可萝尔","text":"请问，您是......新受封的卡西米尔骑士大人吗？","id":180,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/88/Avg_avg_npc_003.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可萝尔","text":"在您解救我们村子之后，会向我们征税吗？","id":181,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/88/Avg_avg_npc_003.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_003","name2":"char_220_grani#3","focus":"2","id":182},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格拉尼","text":"不不不，我可并不是卡西米尔人，更不是什么骑士。","id":183,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d6/Avg_char_220_grani_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格拉尼","text":"虽然维多利亚也有骑士，但我之前是骑警啦！","id":184,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d6/Avg_char_220_grani_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格拉尼","text":"骑警和骑士不一样，是公务治安职务。骑警做事，不图回报，可不会向你们征什么税！","id":185,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d6/Avg_char_220_grani_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_003","name2":"char_220_grani#3","focus":"1","id":186},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可萝尔","text":"维多利亚？","id":187,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/88/Avg_avg_npc_003.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_003","name2":"char_220_grani#3","focus":"2","id":188},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格拉尼","text":"是在卡西米尔外面的地方，我的祖辈也都是从卡西米尔迁到那里去的库兰塔人。","id":189,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d6/Avg_char_220_grani_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格拉尼","text":"这次接到了你们的委托，也是想来卡西米尔看一看，父母的家乡是什么样......没想到会是这么严重的事态。","id":190,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d6/Avg_char_220_grani_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_003","name2":"char_220_grani#3","focus":"1","id":191},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可萝尔","text":"......我本来以为，交给信使的那些委托信都石沉大海了。","id":192,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/88/Avg_avg_npc_003.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可萝尔","text":"毕竟那些民间互助组织从来不会在意我们这偏僻的地方。","id":193,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/88/Avg_avg_npc_003.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_220_grani#4","id":194},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格拉尼","text":"不过，为什么卡西米尔政府没有伸出援手？","id":195,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/9e/Avg_char_220_grani_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_003","name2":"char_220_grani#4","focus":"1","id":196},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可萝尔","text":"哼......首都的骑士大人们怎么会关注我们这种偏远的村子？","id":197,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/88/Avg_avg_npc_003.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可萝尔","text":"正因如此，许多年来，我们反而过得很安稳，城市里动荡不安的生活也不怎么吸引我们。","id":198,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/88/Avg_avg_npc_003.png"},{"type":"character","id":199},{"type":"dialog","id":200},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","block":"true","id":201},{"type":"background","id":202},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","block":"true","id":203},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_ac1_2.png","x":"-100","y":"0","xScale":"1.2","yScale":"1.2","fadetime":"1","screenadapt":"coverall","id":204},{"type":"imagetween","xFrom":"-100","yFrom":"0","xTo":"0","yTo":"0","xScaleFrom":"1.2","yScaleFrom":"1.2","xScaleTo":"1.2","yScaleTo":"1.2","duration":"10","block":"false","id":205},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可萝尔","text":"滴水村的人们世世代代都在这片山区附近居住。","id":206},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可萝尔","text":"尽管生活没那么富裕，但至少我们可以自给自足。","id":207},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可萝尔","text":"虽然有时候会为了躲避天灾暂时迁走村庄，但这里毕竟还是我们的家园。","id":208},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可萝尔","text":"所以，我们无法割舍这片土地......","id":209},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":210},{"type":"character","id":211},{"type":"dialog","id":212},{"type":"image","id":213},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/50/Avg_bg_bg_county_1.png","block":"true","id":214},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":215},{"type":"character","name":"char_220_grani#5","id":216},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格拉尼","text":"但是现在，村子却被那些赏金猎人破坏得满目疮痍——","id":217,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_char_220_grani_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_003","id":218},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可萝尔","text":"......都是因为那个骑士宝藏。","id":219,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/88/Avg_avg_npc_003.png"},{"type":"character","id":220},{"type":"dialog","id":221},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","block":"true","id":222},{"type":"background","id":223},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","block":"true","id":224},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bc/Avg_ac1_1.png","x":"-100","y":"0","xScale":"1.2","yScale":"1.2","fadetime":"1","screenadapt":"coverall","id":225},{"type":"imagetween","xFrom":"-100","yFrom":"0","xTo":"0","yTo":"0","xScaleFrom":"1.2","yScaleFrom":"1.2","xScaleTo":"1.2","yScaleTo":"1.2","duration":"10","block":"false","id":226},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可萝尔","text":"最近几年，附近的几个村落都成了赏金猎人们常常光顾的地方。","id":227},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可萝尔","text":"好像是，卡西米尔北部控制区常有动乱什么的，所以不断有赏金猎人去那里寻找发财的机会，而我们滴水村位于通往北方的必经之路上。","id":228},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可萝尔","text":"本来村子就经常会有赏金猎人出入，但是也没有造成什么危害。","id":229},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可萝尔","text":"直到一个月前，有一伙赏金猎人在山中挖出了一位随从骑士的石棺，还翻出了一小箱陪葬的金币......","id":230},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":231},{"type":"character","id":232},{"type":"dialog","id":233},{"type":"image","id":234},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/50/Avg_bg_bg_county_1.png","block":"true","id":235},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":236},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_003","name2":"char_220_grani#3","focus":"2","id":237},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格拉尼","text":"是这种印着卡西米尔徽章的金币吧？","id":238,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d6/Avg_char_220_grani_1.png"},{"type":"showitem","image":"item_act1_1","id":239},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格拉尼","text":"我刚来这里就有赏金猎人跑来找麻烦，这几枚金币，算做他们举止粗鲁的赔礼。","id":240,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d6/Avg_char_220_grani_1.png"},{"type":"hideitem","id":241},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_003","name2":"char_220_grani#3","focus":"1","id":242},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可萝尔","text":"嗯......就是这些金币，在赏金猎人之间带出了一段传说，也给我们带来了大麻烦。","id":243,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/88/Avg_avg_npc_003.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可萝尔","text":"“卡西米尔的每位古代骑士会带着他们的精神与财富，下葬于其家乡的无名之地，并永世保护着这片土地。”","id":244,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/88/Avg_avg_npc_003.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可萝尔","text":"“只有来自不惧牺牲，无畏艰险的卡西米尔血脉才能破除所有的阻碍。”","id":245,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/88/Avg_avg_npc_003.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可萝尔","text":"这样的传说被传得越来越远，附近的赏金猎人变得越来越多。","id":246,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/88/Avg_avg_npc_003.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可萝尔","text":"最初，赏金猎人还只是讨论如何寻找更大的骑士宝藏，可后来“滴水村有人知道骑士宝藏下落”的消息却不知怎么的越传越开——","id":247,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/88/Avg_avg_npc_003.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_220_grani#5","id":248},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格拉尼","text":"————嘘！大家先别说话！","id":249,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_char_220_grani_5.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":250},{"type":"dialog","id":251},{"type":"character","id":252},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":253},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_soldiersrun","id":254},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赏金猎人","text":"不行，找不到他们，给我从头再搜一遍！","id":255},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$indust_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_bat_indust_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","crossfade":"1.5","id":256,"musicid":3},{"type":"character","name":"char_220_grani#5","id":257},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格拉尼","text":"继续待在这里不太安全，不能拖累这位大叔。","id":258,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_char_220_grani_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格拉尼","text":"总之，我们先离开这里。","id":259,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_char_220_grani_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_005","id":260},{"type":"dialogue","name":"村民","text":"你们要小心点自己的安全，骑士......不对，骑警小姐，村长就交给你了！","id":261,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_npc_005.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_220_grani#2","id":262},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格拉尼","text":"大叔，你放心，我一定保护好——","id":263,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/8f/Avg_char_220_grani_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_220_grani#1","id":264},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格拉尼","text":"啊？村长？","id":265,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e0/Avg_char_220_grani_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_003","id":266},{"type":"dialogue","name":"可萝尔","text":"......滴水村村长可萝尔，虽然上任才半年，就算是我，也是有村长的自尊心的哦。","id":267,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/88/Avg_avg_npc_003.png"},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":268},{"type":"dialog","id":269},{"type":"blocker","block":"true","id":270},{"type":"image","id":271}],"characters":["？？？","赏金猎人","粗暴的赏金猎人","可萝尔","村民","格拉尼"]}